properties.Name: TransunionTradeRecord
properties.Description: TransUnion records of consumer buying and payment activities.

Columns.Name: TransunionReferenceNumber
Columns.Description: The TransUnion file number.

Columns.Name: AccountNumber
Columns.Description:
Consumer's account number with the credit grantor (for consumer protection reasons, partial or truncated account numbers are displayed within the tradelines)
 
May be partially masked with asterisks.

Columns.Name: TradingCompanyName
Columns.Description: The name of the trading company or party.

Columns.Name: TransunionAccountTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a TransUnion account type.

Columns.Name: TransunionResponsibilityTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a TransUnion Responsibility Type.

Columns.Name: OpenedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the trade record was opened.

Columns.Name: ClosedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the trade record was closed.

Columns.Name: Remark
Columns.Description:
A remark associated with the trade record.

Ex:
ACCOUNT IN DISPUTE
CONVENTIONAL MORTGAGE

Columns.Name: CreditLimitAmount
Columns.Description: The credit limit amount associated with the account.

Columns.Name: HighCreditAmount
Columns.Description: Highest amount ever owed by the consumer on that account

Columns.Name: BalanceAmount
Columns.Description: Balance owed as of date verified

Columns.Name: PastDueAmount
Columns.Description: Amount past due as of date verified

Columns.Name: VerifiedDate
Columns.Description: Date of last update on the account

Columns.Name: PaidAmount
Columns.Description: The amount paid upon the account.

Columns.Name: Terms
Columns.Description: The terms associated with the account number.

Columns.Name: LatePaymentNumberOfMonths
Columns.Description: The number of months of late payments.

Columns.Name: LatePayments30Days
Columns.Description: The number of 30 day late payments.

Columns.Name: LatePayments60Days
Columns.Description: The number of 60 day late payments.

Columns.Name: LatePayments90Days
Columns.Description: The number of 90 day late payments.

Columns.Name: DelinquencyDate
Columns.Description: The date that delinquency was declared.

Columns.Name: DelinquencyAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of delinquency.

Columns.Name: PaymentPatternMonths112
Columns.Description:
The subject's payment pattern with his/ her actual rating or Manner of Payment (MOP) over a period of time. Depending on which option a customer chooses either 24 months or 12 months of information will be shown.

Ex:
Months 1 -12: 445543211111

Columns.Name: PaymentPatternMonths324
Columns.Description:
The subject's payment pattern with his/ her actual rating or Manner of Payment (MOP) over a period of time. Depending on which option a customer chooses either 24 months or 12 months of information will be shown.

Ex:
Months 13 -24: 111111111111

Columns.Name: EcoaCode
Columns.Description: The ECOA code.

Columns.Name: TransunionKindOfBusinessClassificationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the TransUnion Kind Of Business Classification.

Columns.Name: TransunionIndustryCodeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a TransUnion Industry Code.
